      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention to be roadworthy again. The engine struggles to maintain a steady idle, there is a noticeable transmission slip between second and third gear, and several body panels show signs of advanced rust and clear coat failure. The interior has seen heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It is ideal for a dedicated mechanic looking for a project or for someone in need of specific spare parts.",
